e $L^p$ estimates as BHT for certain modified bilinear\nand bi-parameter Hilbert transforms with $dim \\, \\Gamma_{1}=dim \\,\n\\Gamma_{2}=1$ but with a slightly better decay than that for the bilinear and\nbi-parameter Hilbert transform (Theorem 1.4).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Mar 2014 22:44:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-01-20"}
