asing fraction of neutral hydrogen\nscattering Lyman-alpha photons, due to cosmic reionization.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Mar 2014 10:09:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 2 May 2014 01:21:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-19"}
